{"type":"message","id":"587bd764","parentId":"e8520194","timestamp":"2026-06-13T13:17:24.689Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"非常关键的发现：\n\n- tts 最近一次 session 是 **6月13日 21:16**，文件 `b6884754-...`——这就是用户说的\"刚刚的对话\"！\n- 06-12 和 06-13 的 memory 文件**不存在**（最新 daily 是 2026-06-09.md）\n- tts 的 MEMORY.md 里 06-13 的 Promoted 区只有 06-09.md 的内容，**没有 06-12/06-13 的数据**\n\n但有个奇怪点：MEMORY.md 的 mtime 显示是 06-13 03:00（dreaming 跑的），而 06-12 之后没有任何 daily 文件。这正好说明：dreaming 在 06-13 03:00 跑了一次\"短时记忆→长期\"提升，但只提到 06-09.md——06-12 之后没有 daily 文件可读，因为 tts 自己没写。\n\n我先读最新这次 session 的实际内容看\"刚跑出来什么数据\"。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_iMlIg7wXpfOXXB44AVm8vr3i","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/b6884754-e119-4101-a476-c467dbda5910.jsonl | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nfor line in sys.stdin:\n    try:\n        obj = json.loads(line)\n        role = obj.get('role', obj.get('type', ''))\n        ts = obj.get('timestamp', '')\n        content = obj.get('content', '')\n        if isinstance(content, list):\n            for c in content:\n                t = c.get('type', '')\n                if t == 'text':\n                    print(f'[{ts}] [{role}] TEXT:', c.get('text', '')[:500])\n                elif t == 'toolCall':\n                    name = c.get('name', c.get('function', {}).get('name', ''))\n                    args = c.get('arguments', c.get('function', {}).get('arguments', ''))\n                    if isinstance(args, dict):\n                        args = json.dumps(args, ensure_ascii=False)\n                    print(f'[{ts}] [{role}] TOOL:', name, str(args)[:300])\n                elif t == 'toolResult':\n                    res = c.get('content', '')\n                    if isinstance(res, list):\n                        res = ' | '.join(str(x)[:200] for x in res)\n                    print(f'[{ts}] [{role}] TOOL_RESULT:', str(res)[:500])\n        else:\n            print(f'[{ts}] [{role}]:', str(content)[:500])\n    except Exception as e:\n        print('ERR:', e)\n\" 2>&1 | head -80"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":1925,"output":578,"cacheRead":66290,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68793,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781356636608,"responseId":"067c8b5df854dd066694f3b7d5cf416c"}}
