{"type":"message","id":"810a132b","parentId":"32cdaca6","timestamp":"2026-06-13T13:57:40.259Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你说的对。tts 不是 cron agent，它是**交互型 agent**（飞书 DM 对话），所以\"每天都写\"对它来说就是\"每场对话结束就写\"，不依赖 cron 触发。\n\ncron 的存在是因为 tts 还跑定时选品扫描（每天 9/12/15/18/21 点），那部分任务没产出 daily 才是真问题——但**用户对话场景**下，应该是每场对话结束 agent 主动记。\n\n回答你第二个问题：先看版本和存储架构现状。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kqgcaddhbosq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw --version 2>&1 | head -5\necho \"---\"\nls /home/halei/.openclaw/ 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\nls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/ 2>/dev/null | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kqgcaddhbosq_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/ 2>/dev/null | head -20\necho \"---\"\ncat /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/package.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print('version:', d.get('version')); print('name:', d.get('name'))\"\necho \"---\"\nwhich openclaw && readlink -f $(which openclaw)"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kqgcaddhbosq_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw update check 2>&1 | head -30 || echo \"update check failed\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":936,"output":357,"cacheRead":74098,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75391,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781359052590,"responseId":"067c94cddb076690c2a04507dba9ffb2"}}
