{"type":"message","id":"9c15bfb2","parentId":"ef70e876","timestamp":"2026-06-13T13:57:54.776Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2pgqwqxofvyx_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OpenClaw 2026.6.1 (2e08f0f) — All your chats, one OpenClaw.\n\nUsage: openclaw update [options] [command]\n\nUpdate OpenClaw and inspect update channel status\n\nOptions:\n  --channel <stable|beta|dev>    Persist update channel (git + npm)\n  --dry-run                      Preview update actions without making changes\n                                 (default: false)\n  -h, --help                     Display help for command\n  --json                         Output result as JSON (default: false)\n  --no-restart                   Skip restarting the gateway service after a\n                                 successful update\n  --tag <dist-tag|version|spec>  Override the package target for this update\n                                 (dist-tag, version, or package spec)\n  --timeout <seconds>            Timeout for each update step in seconds\n                                 (default: 1800)\n  --yes                          Skip confirmation prompts (non-interactive)\n---\n{\n    \"lastCheckedAt\": \"2026-06-13T08:16:22.912Z\",\n    \"lastNotifiedVersion\": \"2026.6.5\",\n    \"lastNotifiedTag\": \"latest\",\n    \"lastAvailableVersion\": \"2026.6.5\",\n    \"lastAvailableTag\": \"latest\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2383,"aggregated":"OpenClaw 2026.6.1 (2e08f0f) — All your chats, one OpenClaw.\n\nUsage: openclaw update [options] [command]\n\nUpdate OpenClaw and inspect update channel status\n\nOptions:\n  --channel <stable|beta|dev>    Persist update channel (git + npm)\n  --dry-run                      Preview update actions without making changes\n                                 (default: false)\n  -h, --help                     Display help for command\n  --json                         Output result as JSO