ace because shared SQLite state has conflicting plugin install metadata for: feishu, lossless-claw, openclaw-lark, openclaw-weixin, wecom-openclaw-plugin\n│\n◇  Doctor warnings ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                        │\n│  - Left plugin install index in place because shared SQLite state has  │\n│    conflicting plugin install metadata for: feishu, lossless-claw,     │\n│    openclaw-lark, openclaw-weixin, wecom-openclaw-plugin               │\n│                                                                        │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\nMemory Search (main)\nProvider: openai (requested: openai)\nModel: openai\nSources: memory\nIndexed: 133/168 files · 2071 chunks\nDirty: yes\nStore: ~/.openclaw/memory/main.sqlite\nWorkspace: ~/.openclaw/workspace\n---\nmemory-core config keys: ['dreaming']\ndreaming enabled: True\ndreaming frequency: None\n---\nplugins.allow: ['browser', 'lossless-claw', 'memory-core', 'minimax', 'openclaw-lark', 'openclaw-weixin', 'openrouter', 'wecom-openclaw-plugin', 'workboard', 'searxng']"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9473,"aggregated":"Config warnings:\n- plugins.entries.feishu: plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected; global plugin will be overridden by global plugin (/home/halei/.openclaw/npm/projects/openclaw-feishu-dc69f44688/node_modules/@openclaw/feishu/dist/index.js)\n- plugins.entries.feishu: plugin disabled (disabled in config) but config is present\n│\n◇  Doctor warnings ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                        │\n│  - Left plugin install index in place because shared SQLite state has  │\n│    conflicting plugin install metadata for: feishu, lossless-claw,     │\n│    openclaw-lark, openclaw-weixin, wecom-openclaw-plugin               │\n│                             