{"type":"message","id":"d1844942","parentId":"13263767","timestamp":"2026-06-13T14:21:19.472Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"搞定。同步通知工部——让他把这次新发现（两个 agent 没 IDENTITY）也记到他的工作流里，以后配置 agent 时主动检查 IDENTITY.md 是否完整。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fal05zn73dgt_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"agentId":"agent-orchestrator","message":"## 补充：花名册规则 + IDENTITY 检查项\n\n### 1. 花名册（已写入 main MEMORY.md）\n10 个 agent 中文名 + emoji 如下，从现在起所有对话都按这个叫：\n\n| agent_id | 名字 | emoji |\n|----------|------|-------|\n| main | KIIT（大总管） | 🪶 |\n| agent-orchestrator | 工部 | 🔧 |\n| tts | TK 选品大师 | — |\n| content | TK 内容专家 | 🎬 |\n| koc | TK 达人专家 | 🤝 |\n| traffic | TK 投流专家 | 🚀 |\n| ops | TK 运营助手 | ✅ |\n| director | TK 运营总监 | 📊 |\n| finance | TK 财务专家 | 💰 |\n| review | TK 客服专家 | 💬 |\n\nHALEI 原话：「所有的agent我都给定义了名字了吧，或者是飞书机器人都名字，你以后都用这个，我好知道是谁。」\n\n### 2. 你（工部）的额外任务\n- 你自己 / KIIT 的 IDENTITY.md 我已补完（KIIT/工部 + emoji）\n- 其他 8 个业务 agent（tts/content/koc/traffic/ops/director/finance/review）的 IDENTITY.md 由 HALEI 早前已建好，确认存在即可\n- 以后**新建/调整 agent 时**，IDENTITY.md 是必填项（不能留模板），写进你的工作流铁律\n\n### 3. 任务 A/B 照常执行\n花名册这条不阻塞你改 SOUL 铁律和 dreaming fallback 的事。继续。","timeoutSeconds":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":53,"output":434,"cacheRead":96233,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96720,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781360470313,"responseId":"067c9a57a36310b3225f9e1aaee2536f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e766aea0","parentId":"d1844942","timestamp":"2026-06-13T14:22:09.178Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_fal05zn73dgt_1","toolName":"sessions_send","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"runId\": \"b36a989f-075f-4426-8c6a-b0ec0cafd1f6\",\n  \"status\": \"ok\",\n  \"reply\": \"所有 IDENTITY.md 确认完毕。状态回报：\\n\\n**✅ 花名册已收到** — 10 个 agent 中文名 + emoji 已记录，后续对话全部按此叫。\\n\\n**✅ IDENTITY.md 检查结果 — 9/9 存在：**\\n- tts ✅、content ✅、koc ✅、traffic ✅、ops ✅、director ✅、finance ✅、review ✅\\n- 工部（agent-orchestrator）✅\\n\\n**📋 当前任务状态：**\\n- **Task A**（10 个 SOUL.md 写记忆铁律）：✅ 已完成\\n- **Task B**（dreaming fallback sessionIngest）：❌ 字段在 schema 中不存在，`config.patch` 拒绝写入\\n- **花名册规则**：已纳入工作记忆，新建/调整 agent 时 IDENTITY.md 必填\\n\\nTask B 阻塞无变化，等 HALEI 确认是否换方案。\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:agent-orchestrator:main\",\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"mode\": \"announce\"\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"runId":"b36a989f-075f-4426-8c6a-b0ec0cafd1f6","status":"ok","reply":"所有 IDENTITY.md 确认完毕。状态回报：\n\n**✅ 花名册已收到** — 10 个 agent 中文名 + emoji 已记录，后续对话全部按此叫。\n\n**✅ IDENTITY.md 检查结果 — 9/9 存在：**\n- tts ✅、content ✅、koc ✅、traffic ✅、ops ✅、director ✅、finance ✅、review ✅\n- 工部（agent-orchestrator）✅\n\n**📋 当前任务状态：**\n- **Task A**（10 个 SOUL.md 写记忆铁律）：✅ 已完成\n- **Task B**（dreaming fallback sessionIngest）：❌ 字段在 schema 中不存在，`config.patch` 拒绝写入\n- **花名册规则**：已纳入工作记忆，新建/调整 agent 时 IDENTITY.md 必填\n\nTask B 阻塞无变化，等 HALEI 确认是否换方案。","sessionKey":"agent:agent-orchestrator:main","delivery":{"status":"pending","mode":"announce"}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781360529171}}
{"type":"message","id":"d13c156c","parentId":"e766aea0","timestamp":"2026-06-13T14:22:18.267Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"工部回报：\n- ✅ Task A 完成（10 个 SOUL.md 都加了铁律）\n- ❌ Task B 阻塞——`sessionIngest` 字段在 schema 里不存在\n- ✅ 花名册 / IDENTITY.md 检查完毕\n\n**Task B 阻塞需要你拍板**——`dreaming.sessionIngest` 这个字段在我之前的方案里是猜的，实际 memory-core 6.1 没有这个配置。工部已经按规矩 `config.patch` 拒绝写入没验证过的字段（这是好事，**不瞎改配置**）。\n\n我看一下 dream 实际支持的配置项，给个可落地的备选。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vrka3b00ad5p_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\nmc = d.get('plugins', {}).get('entries', {}).get('memory-core', {}).get('config', {})\nprint('current memory-core config:')\nprint(json.dumps(mc, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vrka3b00ad5p_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw -name \"memory-core*\" 2>/dev/null | head -10\necho \"---\"\nfind /home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw -path \"*/memory-core/*\" -name \"*.json\" 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":313,"output":329,"cacheRead":96706,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97348,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781360530278,"responseId":"067c9a942beb575b541abbf0f5e184d1"}}
