{"type":"message","id":"10865e46","parentId":"bd66ae6f","timestamp":"2026-06-13T14:22:25.385Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dbexqmjqr5vz_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"memory-core\",\n  \"activation\": {\n    \"onStartup\": false\n  },\n  \"kind\": \"memory\",\n  \"contracts\": {\n    \"memoryEmbeddingProviders\": [\n      \"local\"\n    ],\n    \"tools\": [\n      \"memory_get\",\n      \"memory_search\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"commandAliases\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"dreaming\",\n      \"kind\": \"runtime-slash\",\n      \"cliCommand\": \"memory\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"uiHints\": {\n    \"dreaming.frequency\": {\n      \"label\": \"Dreaming Frequency\",\n      \"placeholder\": \"0 3 * * *\",\n      \"help\": \"Optional cron cadence for the full dreaming sweep (light, REM, then deep).\"\n    },\n    \"dreaming.model\": {\n      \"label\": \"Dreaming Model\",\n      \"placeholder\": \"anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6\",\n      \"help\": \"Optional provider/model override for Dream Diary narrative subagent runs. Requires plugins.entries.memory-core.subagent.allowModelOverride.\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"configSchema\": {\n    \"type\": \"object\",\n    \"additionalProperties\": false,\n    \"properties\": {\n      \"dreaming\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"additionalProperties\": false,\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"enabled\": {\n            \"type\": \"boolean\"\n          },\n          \"frequency\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"model\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"timezone\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"verboseLogging\": {\n            \"type\": \"boolean\"\n          },\n          \"storage\": {\n            \"type\": \"object\",\n            \"additionalProperties\": false,\n            \"properties\": {\n              \"mode\": {\n                \"type\": \"string\",\n                \"enum\": [\n                  \"inline\",\n                  \"separate\",\n                  \"both\"\n                ]\n              },\n              \"separateReports\": {\n                \"type\": \"boolean\"\n              }\n            }\n          },\n          \"execution\": {\n            \"type\": \"object\",\n            \"additionalProperties\": false,\n            \"properties\": {\n              \"defaults\": {\n                \"type\": \"object\",\n                \"additionalProperties\": false,\n                \"properties\": {\n                  \"model\": {\n                    \"type\": \"string\"\n                  }\n                }\n              }\n            }\n          },\n          \"phases\": {\n            \"type\": \"object\",\n            \"additionalProperties\": false,\n            \"properties\": {\n              \"light\": {\n                \"type\": \"object\",\n                \"additionalProperties\": false,\n                \"properties\": {\n                  \"enabled\": {\n                    \"type\": \"boolean\"\n                  },\n                  \"lookbackDays\": {\n                    \"type\": \"integer\",\n                    \"minimum\": 0\n                  },\n                  \"limit\": {\n                    \"type\": \"integer\",\n                    \"minimum\": 0\n                  },\n                  \"dedupeSimilarity\": {\n                    \"type\": \"number\",\n                    \"minimum\": 0,\n                    \"maximum\": 1\n                  },\n                  \"execution\": {\n                    \"type\": \"object\",\n                    \"additionalProperties\": false,\n                    \"properties\": {\n                      \"model\": {\n                        \"type\": \"string\"\n                      }\n                    }\n                  }\n                }\n              },\n              \"deep\": {\n                \"type\": \"object\",\n                \"additionalProperties\": false,\n                \"properties\": {\n                  \"enabled\": {\n                    \"type\": \"boolean\"\n                  },\n                  \"limit\": {\n                    \"type\": \"integer\",\n                    \"minimum\": 0\n                  },\n                  \"minScore\": {\n                    \"type\": \"number\",\n                    \"minimum\": 0,\n                    \"maximum\": 1\n                  },\n                  \"minRecallCount\": {\n                    \"type\": \"integer\",\n                    \"minimum\": 0\n                  },\n                  \"minUniqueQueries\": {\n                    \"type\": \"integer\",\n                    \"minimum\": 0\n                  },\n                  \"recencyHalfLifeDays\": {\n                    \"type\": \"integer\",\n                    \"minimum\": 0\n                  },\n                  \"maxAgeDays\": {\n                    \"type\": \"integer\",\n                    \"minimum\": 1\n                  },\n                  \"maxPromotedSnippetTokens\": {\n                    \"type\": \"integer\",\n                    \"minimum\": 1,\n                    \"description\": \"Maximum estimated token count for each short-term recall snippet promoted into MEMORY.md. Provenance metadata remains attached to the entry.\"\n                  },\n                  \"execution\": {\n                    \"type\": \"object\",\n                    \"additionalProperties\": false,\n                    \"properties\": {\n                      \"model\": {\n                        \"type\": \"string\"\n                      }\n                    }\n                  }\n                }\n              },\n              \"rem\": {\n                \"type\": \"object\",\n                \"additionalProperties\": false,\n                \"properties\": {\n                  \"enabled\": {\n                    \"type\": \"boolean\"\n                  },\n                  \"lookbackDays\": {\n                    \"type\": \"integer\",\n                    \"minimum\": 0\n                  },\n                  \"limit\": {\n                    \"type\": \"integer\",\n                    \"minimum\": 0\n                  },\n                  \"minPatternStrength\": {\n                    \"type\": \"number\",\n                    \"minimum\": 0,\n                    \"maximum\": 1\n                  },\n                  \"execution\": {\n                    \"type\": \"object\",\n                    \"additionalProperties\": false,\n                    \"properties\": {\n                      \"model\": {\n                        \"type\": \"string\"\n                      }\n                    }\n                  }\n                }\n              }\n            }\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781360545284}}
{"type":"message","id":"a361bc9a","parentId":"10865e46","timestamp":"2026-06-13T14:22:38.946Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到了——**6.1 这个版本的 memory-core 根本不支持从 session jsonl 自动回填 daily**。`dreaming` 下的所有合法配置都列在上面了，没有 `sessionIngest` 之类的字段。\n\n**dreaming 实际吃的\"原料\"是 daily memory 文件**——没 daily 它就跑空，这是设计如此。**没有官方 fallback 机制**（要等 6.5+ 才有，或换 QMD / Honcho / memory-wiki 后端）。\n\n我把这件事如实告诉工部，让他用**现有合法字段**做到\"接近 fallback\"的效果，然后给你两套方案选。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1b469pghoq15_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"agentId":"agent-orchestrator","message":"## 澄清：Task B（dreaming fallback）问题\n\n查了 memory-core 6.1 的 `configSchema`：`dreaming` 下**没有** `sessionIngest` 这个字段。你 `config.patch` 拒绝写入是对的。\n\n合法字段只有：\n- `enabled`、`frequency`、`model`、`timezone`、`verboseLogging`\n- `storage.mode / storage.separateReports`\n- `phases.light.*`（lookbackDays、limit、dedupeSimilarity）\n- `phases.deep.*`（minScore、minRecallCount、minUniqueQueries、recencyHalfLifeDays、maxAgeDays、maxPromotedSnippetTokens）\n- `phases.rem.*`\n\n**6.1 版本没有\"从 session jsonl 自动回填 daily\"的能力**，这是 6.5+ 才有 / 需要换后端（QMD/Honcho）的能力。\n\n### 我已经做的事\n把这个问题在 KIIT 这边挂起，等 HALEI 拍板——三选一：\n- A：升 6.5+（HALEI 之前说不升 6.6，但 6.5 跳 4 版没专门查过，可能 6.5 有这个能力？需你查 6.5 changelog）\n- B：换 memory 后端（QMD / Honcho）但工作量大\n- C：放弃机器 fallback，**靠 Task A 的 SOUL 铁律 + KIIT 这边抽查**兜底\n\n### 你的下一步\n- Task A 已完成 ✅\n- Task B **暂时挂起**，不写任何无效配置\n- 等 HALEI 三选一拍板\n\n回报时同步给 HALEI：「Task A 完成；Task B 因 6.1 schema 不支持 sessionIngest，挂起等拍板」。","timeoutSeconds":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":1161,"output":548,"cacheRead":97729,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99438,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781360545509,"responseId":"067c9aa2c98bffa91a7cfda05ec6c4d1"}}
