{"type":"message","id":"9d5a3eec","parentId":"08f1915b","timestamp":"2026-06-13T14:23:33.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"看到截图了——你飞书里设的名字跟我现在用的有两处对不上，得统一一下。\n\n## 你飞书里的实际名字 vs MEMORY.md 里的名字\n\n| agent_id | 飞书显示 | MEMORY.md 写的 | 是否一致 |\n|----------|----------|----------------|----------|\n| tts | **TK 选品大师** | TK 选品大师 | ✅ |\n| traffic | **TK 投流专家** | TK 投流专家 | ✅ |\n| director | **TK 运营总监** | TK 运营总监 | ✅ |\n| content | **TK 内容专家** | TK 内容专家 | ✅ |\n| koc | **TK 达人运营** | TK 达人专家 | ❌ 截图里是\"运营\"，我写的是\"专家\" |\n| review | **TK 客服专家** | TK 客服专家 | ✅ |\n| ops | **TK 运营助手** | TK 运营助手 | ✅ |\n| finance | **TK 财务助手** | TK 财务专家 | ❌ 截图里是\"助手\"，我写的是\"专家\" |\n\n**两处不一致**：\n- koc：飞书是 **TK 达人运营**，我写成了\"达人专家\"\n- finance：飞书是 **TK 财务助手**，我写成了\"财务专家\"\n\n我先修正 MEMORY.md（以你飞书飞书机器人的实际名为准），再让工部把 IDENTITY.md 也同步过去。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jcm0kow5rlrr_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md","edits":[{"oldText":"| koc | TK 达人专家 | koc | 🤝 |","newText":"| koc | TK 达人运营 | koc | 🤝 |"},{"oldText":"| finance | TK 财务专家 | finance | 💰 |","newText":"| finance | TK 财务助手 | finance | 💰 |"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":101282,"output":462,"cacheRead":114,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101858,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781360601225,"responseId":"067c9ad9c5df4534964208bf8b5491d9"}}
